Review summary
Powered by AI
Location:The hotel is conveniently located near tram lines and Docklands attractions, offering easy access to the CBD and nearby dining spots. It's set in a comfortable part of Docklands with a shopping center nearby, making it ideal for both leisure and business travelers.(based on 73 reviews)
Service Quality:Guests consistently praise the friendly and attentive staff, especially at the front desk. The service is described as professional and welcoming, with staff willing to go the extra mile to assist guests, including late-night requests.(based on 35 reviews)
Facilities:The hotel features excellent facilities such as a pool, spa, gym, and sauna. Guests appreciate the modern amenities and well-maintained public areas. The breakfast is also highly rated, offering a variety of options.(based on 42 reviews)
Room Quality:Rooms are described as stylish, modern, and offering scenic views, particularly of the harbor and city. Although some guests noted minor cleanliness issues, many found the rooms comfortable and well-equipped.(based on 73 reviews)

Property Description

  • Number of Rooms: 273
Phone:+61-3-85780000
Email:docklands@vibehotels.com.au
Vibe Hotel Melbourne Docklands is centrally located in Melbourne, a 1-minute walk from The District Docklands and 13 minutes by foot from Marvel Stadium. This hotel is 1.3 mi (2.1 km) from Queen Victoria Market and 1.7 mi (2.7 km) from Crown Casino.

Take advantage of recreational opportunities offered, including an outdoor pool, a hot tub, and a sauna. This hotel also features complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and a television in a common area.

Satisfy your appetite for lunch or dinner at the hotel's restaurant, DOCK 18, or stay in and take advantage of the room service (during limited hours). Quench your thirst with your favorite drink at the bar/lounge. Full breakfasts are served on weekdays from 6:30 AM to 10:30 AM and on weekends from 7:00 AM to 11:00 AM for a fee.

Featured amenities include limo/town car service, express check-in, and express check-out. Planning an event in Melbourne? This hotel has 3875 square feet (360 square meters) of space consisting of conference space and 7 meeting rooms.

Make yourself at home in one of the 273 air-conditioned rooms featuring LCD televisions. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms have complimentary toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include phones, as well as safes and desks.
